\title{Alife}

\taxon{skill}

\meta{description}{Comprehensive Artificial Life skill combining ALIFE2025 proceedings, classic texts (Axelrod, Epstein-Axtell), ALIEN simulation, Lenia, NCA, swarm intelligence, and evolutionary computation. 337 pages extracted, 80+ papers, 153 figures.}

